10. Challenges & Solutions
Challenge 1: Small Dataset
Issue: Only 10 houses limits learning
Solution: Documented limitation, suggested data expansion
Challenge 2: Categorical Encoding
Issue: Initially used wrong encoding (label encoding)
Solution: Switched to One-Hot Encoding
Challenge 3: Limited Test Set
Issue: Only 2 test samples
Solution: Used random_state for reproducibility, documented need for cross-validation
Challenge 4: Feature Scaling
Issue: Different scales (sqft vs rooms)
Solution: Linear Regression handles this, but noted for future algorithms
Challenge 5: Input Validation
Issue: No handling for invalid locations
Solution: Documented valid inputs, planned validation for v2.0
